metatab-latest: Variance replicate estimate tables include estimates, margins of error, and 80 variance replicates for selected American Community Survey 5-year Detailed Tables. The tables are intended for advanced users who are adding ACS data within a table or between geographies. This package contains the state average weights and k values for use in some calculations.
